    Real-Time Photo Access

    Delight Your Guests With
    Instant Photo Delivery

    Guests scan a QR code to view the Instant Gallery, with multiple access
    options available:

    Open Access

    Anyone with the QR Code can access the entire Instant Gallery. The most popular setting. Best for social, public, or inclusive gatherings.

    Selfie Access

    Guests unlock a private gallery by taking a selfie — showing only their own photos. Best for 1 to 1 and high-privacy delivery.

    Face Match

    Guests tap their faces to search for their own photos. A fast search option for large galleries or high-volume events.

    Password Protection

    Set a password for extra privacy and prevent non-guests from accessing. Best for controlled or invitation-only events.
